my facial at @mylittlewaxbar was divine! i loved every second of this session and wish it lasted longer. ive been in front of the camera every day and the heavy lights and sometimes wearing makeup can stress the skin. i love skincare and take great pride in the health of my skin. i feel it’s important to keep your skin healthy over anything else. many days i go without makeup or very little because i really made a conscious effort to pay attention to what my skin needs. i wear sunscreen daily, eat the healthiest i can and use only natural, organic products to ensure my skin get what it deserves. now i need to add my little wax bar facial to the list of things to do to keep my skin glowing. 

.
.
.

use my code MISSSONYANICOLE10 to book an appointment with my little wax bar and get some money off of your facial. 

.
.
.
ps. my voice was nearly gone while recording my voice over so don’t judge me!

@mylittlewaxbar 

.
.
skincare is one of my favorite things. i live for a good moisturizer and serum. even though i an melanated i wear sunscreen daily. it’s so important. i live for clear health skin. makeup foundations are much better when your skin is healthy underneath. this is my second facial in my life and i must say i need to keep up with these every month. makeup is great but healthy skin is a winner. i can’t wait until my next session. the glow was so real and my skin looked even better days later. 

.
.
.
use code MISSSONYA10 for 10% off of your facial!

Runway Resilience: Building A Skin Positive Mindset.
these are photos from my very first book that is now published and ready for print and e book form on Amazon, Barnes & Noble, Kobo and more!. 
..
check out my official site to purchase this e book as well as other merch! if you would like this in print please grab one on Amazon or Barnes & Noble! 

.
.
anyone who knows me know i love skincare! it’s been a love of mine from an early age. i take great pride in caring for my skin the best way possible. natural and organic ingredients make a difference in the health of your skin and a good diet and morning and night routines will always be the way to go. my goal in this book was to give tips and tricks on how i keep my skin healthy but also the confidence it takes to be in the modeling industry. i hope this read finds you well and my wish is for all to have a positive mindset no matter your where life is leading you! 

.
.
love + light 
Sonya ❤️

Glowing Beyond: Melanin in the Beauty Industry. 

.
.
this is my second book about skincare with an emphasis on melanated skin. it’s available on all major platforms such a Amazon & Barnes & Noble in e-book and paperback form. you can also visit my official website to purchase this book in e-book form..MISSSONYANICOLE.COM

.
.
this book sits extremely close to me being a black woman in the industry. when i started as a child in the business it wasn’t easy. in a business where you aren’t deemed the most desirable on screen and in photos it can be tough. but i had to grow and gain the confidence that everyone needs and should have to succeed in any field. this book touches on the history of black woman in the industry as well as how to protect, care and love our beautiful melanated skin. i detailed many black skincare products i currently use and those that are making waves in the skincare industry. i hope this read finds you well and that you always have the confidence to keep going, believing and being all that you can be..

.
.
love + light
Sonya 🩷
